THE NEW PIECES ARE OUT!
We are very proud of this mini capsule of two awesome designs, both titled BUNNY SUIT, a monster to hide in, fluffy armour to fend from within. 
We have been hibernating and working on lots of new designs and this is what we are hoping to be the first of many drops this year.
The items are online now and every bit of support goes miles for us, we are still working from the same  bedrooms and doing our best to keep the spirit of this special project alive. Lots of love and enjoy
